This is a Django application allowing to index and then browse instalations of
Solaris packages.

Generating ANTLR parser
-----------------------

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
java -classpath /path/to/antlr-3.1.2.jar org.antlr.Tool pkginfo.g
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Populating the database
-----------------------

Get the output of pkginfo.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
solarisbox=fqdn.yourdomain.com
ssh ${solarisbox} pkginfo -l > ${solarisbox}.pkginfo
ssh ${solarisbox} showrev -p > ${solarisbox}.showrev
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Execute Django shell

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./manage.py shell
from solaris.packages import MachineEnumerator
me = MachineEnumerator("fqdn.yourdomain.com")
me.Executify()
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Importing patch installation information
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./manage.py shell
from solaris import packages
pm = packages.PatchEnumerator("fqdn.yourdomain.com")
pm.PopulateDatabase()
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
